{"tid":460024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(幫港出聲) 雷鼎鳴：內地朋友「叫雞」都可手機付款, 生活方便過香港","createTime":"2017-11-06T09:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T08:59:52.000Z","uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"d59fbb5bea8763a6a377cf60ff7c3dd6d315582f","tid":460024,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T09:43:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171106/57425269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171106%2F57425269&d=LGXF8pnRWKgDDRU%2FAc5FZ5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=96eccddd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171106%2F57425269&h=765c3d1b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171106/57425269</a><br />\n<br />\n雷鼎鳴稱不會「支爆」：內地叫雞都可手機付款 生活方便過香港<br />\n<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 1106 16:45<br />\n <br />\n朱永倫攝 <br />\n<br />\n香港科技大學經濟系前系主任及榮休教授雷鼎鳴今日出席以「國家與香港」為題的研討會指，香港部分人認為國家經濟會冧，支持港獨，有人甚至以「支爆」形容國家面臨的危機，但他認為內地經濟不會爆煲。<br />\n<br />\n雷鼎鳴指，在內地捐錢給乞丐、「叫雞」也可以透過手機付款，來說明內地生活十分方便，遠超香港，「有事實擺喺度，你就算冇掌握數據，你走去大陸行吓啦，你點見到（經濟）有咩會冧，科技上面嘅進步，學術論文嘅增長，大陸生活程度方便過香港，你畀錢乞兒，都可以攞部手機出嚟照一照，我識得朋友叫雞（召妓）嘅，佢話叫雞都可以拎部手機出嚟照，香港呢啲嘢仲未做得到」。"},{"pid":"09ace256095f7c7fe0e6debf37be04b1895139bf","tid":460024,"uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T09:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3638e25d412f63182d547e7983773a0b90e16c61","tid":460024,"uid":23951,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T09:44:22.000Z","msg":"朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c4c7c674190bc650bc59828ac2fbea7f62416d","tid":460024,"uid":153318,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T09:44:44.000Z","msg":"你朋友，即係你"},{"pid":"b50737f80aa853e998d8f8af9c66ec2763045ace","tid":4